/PeteTongIbiza-Classics-arena-tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTongIbiza-Classics-arena-tour-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTongIbiza-Classics-arena-tour-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTongIbiza-Classics-arena-tour-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTongIbiza-Classics-arena-tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTongIbiza-Classics-arena-tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-tong">皮特·汤 (Pete Tong)</a>宣布与朱尔斯·巴克利 (Jules Buckley) 和 Essential Orchestra 一起进行“伊维萨经典”英国舞台巡演。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><p>这位 DJ 兼广播公司在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bbc">BBC</a>广播电台 1 主持<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b006wkfp/episodes/player" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Essential Mix</em></a> ，他将于 2025 年末将他广受好评的节目带到英国的六个舞台，以庆祝其成立 10 周年。</p><p>即将到来的演出将于 12 月 4 日在格拉斯哥拉开帷幕，接下来还将在诺丁汉、曼彻斯特、利兹和伯明翰停留。这次徒步旅行计划于 12 月 12 日和 13 日在伦敦 The O2 举行两场演出作为结束。</p><p> Tong 将与他的长期合作者 Jules Buckley 和 Essential Orchestra 一起登台演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3821538" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3821538" style="width: 2500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3821538" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTong-Ibiza-Classics-tour.jpg" alt="Pete Tong 的“伊维萨经典”英国巡演" width="2500" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTong-Ibiza-Classics-tour.jpg 2500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTong-Ibiza-Classics-tour-400x203.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTong-Ibiza-Classics-tour-800x406.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTong-Ibiza-Classics-tour-696x354.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/PeteTong-Ibiza-Classics-tour-1392x707.jpg 1392w, https://www.