”</a> 。据说这位 DJ 目前正在创作新音乐。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-tong-announces-ibiza-classics-2025-uk-arena-tour-with-jules-buckley-and-the-essential-orchestra-buy-tickets-3821522">Pete Tong 宣布与 Jules Buckley 和 The Essential Orchestra 合作的“伊维萨经典”2025 年英国竞技场巡演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
